  "keyFeatures": [
    "Interactive map with building and event markers powered by Leaflet",
    "Turn-by-turn route calculation between campus buildings",
    "Role-based access control for students and administrators",
    "Admin dashboard for managing buildings, events, and classrooms",
    "Real-time analytics with charts for usage, accesses, and popular routes",
    "User registration with admin approval workflow",
    "Dark mode support with a consistent design system",
    "Full-text search across buildings and events"
